9368">Tweeting a photo via MMS</a></li><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a data-article="20170024" href="/articles/20170024">Twitter&#39;s supported mobile carriers</a></li></ul></li><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a class="has-articles" data-category="301" href="#"><i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i><span>mobile.twitter.com</span></a></li><li class="leftnav-item" role="menuitem"><a class="leftnav-back" href="#"><i class="fa fa-chevron-left"></i> Back</a></li></ul></li>
